Package com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport Description

Contains classes for communicating schema information with i2 Analyze services that interact with the Analysis Repository.

In the i2 Analyze API, the ItemType class is the parent of EntityType and LinkType. The EntityType and LinkType classes contain the PropertyTypes and PropertyGroupTypes that those classes use.

Similar to the relationships between items, entities, and links, the common methods of entity types and link types are implemented in the ItemType class. Just as links record what entities they connect, so link types record what entity types they can connect.

Since:
1.0
